=== WOUNDED_SOLDIER ===
# id: 45
# title: The Wounded Soldier
# chinese_title: 伤兵
# category: Crew
# mode: dungeon

You find a soldier from a patrol unit slumped against the wall, clutching a wound in her side. Her squad was ambushed and scattered. She asks for medical help and offers to share intel on the area ahead in return.

* [Treat her wounds with your supplies]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  "人" (rén) — person, people
* [Give her a med-hypo]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "伤" (shāng) — wound, injury, to hurt
* [Ask for intel first, then help]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "先" (xiān) — first, before
* [Leave her — you can't risk it]
  ~ nothing
  "弃" (qì) — to abandon
